{
  "id": "adv_group_moon_03_05",
  "title": "月のテンペスト 03 05",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cafe-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "……ていう感じかなー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Something like that~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、なんと言いますか……\nあなたも苦労してきたんですのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ how should I put it…\nYou've been through a lot too‚ haven't you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 10.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "そうかなー？\nみんなそれぞれいろいろあるんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really~?\nDoesn't everyone have their own struggles?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "それはそうでしょうけど……\nなんだか私よりずっと達観してますわね、芽衣は",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true‚ but…\nYou seem much more detached than I am‚ Mei.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 23.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "なんというか……このドーナツ、お食べになって？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here… have this donut.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "え、いいの？　ありがとー！　一杯喋ったから\nお腹空いちゃってさー！　んふ～、美味しいな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh‚ really? Thanks~! I'm starving\nafter talking so much~! Mmm~‚ delicious~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.5666641235
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "まったく……\n芽衣は、ずっと明るくて、優しかったのですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly…\nYou've always been cheerful and kind‚ haven't you‚ Mei?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.0999974568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.3666641235
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "んー？　すずにゃん、今何か言った？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm~? Suzu-nyan‚ did you say something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.3666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.2666641235
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "なんでもないですわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It was nothing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.2666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.2666641235
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣はずっとこんな感じだよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've always been like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.2666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.1999974568
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "聞こえてるなら初めからそう言いなさい！\nなんで一度泳がせたんですの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you heard me‚ then why didn't you say so from the beginning!\nWhy did you pretend not to hear?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.5333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.5333307902
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、そういえば……部長にアイドルを選んだ理由は\n聞かれなかったんですの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ by the way… did the captain ask you\nwhy you chose to be an idol?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.4333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.2999974568
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "ちゃんと伝えたよ。アイドルを選んだのはね～\nすずにゃんのおかげなんだ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I told her. I chose to be an idol because~\nit's thanks to Suzu-nyan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.6666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.9666625976
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　わ、私？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh? M-me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.9666625976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.0333277384
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ね、中学からはいろんな部活のヘルプに行ったし\n友達も結構一杯いたと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You see‚ in middle school‚ I helped out with a lot of different clubs‚\nand I think I had quite a few friends.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.5666610717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.8666641235
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、誰か一人とすっごく仲良くなることって\nなかったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I never became really close\nwith anyone.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.9666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "だからかな、すずにゃんが「ずっと一緒に」って\n言ってくれた時……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe that's why‚ when Suzunyān said‚\n\"Let's always be together\"…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.2666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.4333307902
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "なんだか胸がぽかぽかして、ふわーって軽くなったの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I felt this warmth in my chest‚ and everything felt lighter!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.4333307902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 110.2333307902
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "それで「あ、芽衣はこの子と一緒に頑張りたいな」って\n思ったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I thought‚ \"Ah‚ I‚ Mei‚ want to work hard\nwith this girl.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.6666641235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.2999959309
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それだけですの？　私だって、そういうことを\n言ったとかろうじて覚えているくらいですわよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "T-that's all? I barely even remember\nsaying that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.7999959309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.6666605631
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃんが覚えてなくても\n芽衣はちゃーんと覚えてるよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if you don't remember‚ Suzu-nyan‚\nI remember it clearly!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.9666600544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.0666605631
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "それに、きっかけなんてそんなものじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Besides‚ it's not like a reason is necessary‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.0666605631,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
      "startTime": 135.1999832152
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_03_05-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣は嬉しかったんだ。あんな風に\n芽衣を必要としてくれるのが……本当に、本当に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was happy. I was truly‚ truly happy\nthat you needed me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.6333099364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_donutsshop-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "donutsshop-00-noon",
